*(''easy to like: thing''): [[horrible]], [[horrid]], [[nasty]]
*(''having a pleasant taste or aroma''): [[awful]], [[disgusting]], [[foul]], [[horrible]], [[horrid]], [[nasty]], [[nauseating]], [[putrid]], [[rancid]], [[rank]], [[sickening]]
